      "weight": "500",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "RESOURCES CURATED",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "18px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "600+",
      "font": "Lora",
      "size": "60px",
      "weight": "500",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "HOURS OF ORGANIZED CONTENT",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "18px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "COMMUNITY IN ACTIVE IMPLEMENTATION",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "18px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "Why did I build Mycelium at 16?",
      "font": "Cormorant Garamond",
      "size": "39px",
      "weight": "500",
      "color": "rgb(250, 247, 240)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "I built Mycelium at 16 because I wanted uncomplicated permaculture guidance. I got exhausted finding conflicting advice and resources that didn’t apply to me. So I spent the next year building a platf",
      "font": "Cormorant Garamond",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "700",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "How We Operate",
      "font": "Cormorant Garamond",
      "size": "60px",
      "weight": "500",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "We prioritize transparency with all our users, we want you to know how we create resources and build this platform.",
      "font": "Cormorant Garamond",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "500",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "Zero Gatekeeping",
      "font": "Lora",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "600",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "100% Free, forever. No paywalls, no ads interrupting your learning. We believe that permaculture knowledge should should be accessible to everyone, regardless of income or location",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "We verify every resource",
      "font": "Lora",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "600",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "We personally review every video, course, and article before adding it to Mycelium. Each resource is checked thoroughly, prioritizing beginner-friendliness.",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H1",
      "text": "We work with expert partners",
      "font": "Lora",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "600",
      "color": "rgb(255, 255, 255)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "Our resources are credible and field-tested – built in partnership with the Baganihan Collective and shaped by contributions from the Philippine Permaculture Association (PPA)",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "24px",
      "weight": "400",
      "color": "rgb(210, 206, 200)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "H2",
      "text": "Curated Permaculture Videos",
      "font": "Outfit",
      "size": "48px",
      "weight": "700",
      "color": "rgb(36, 36, 36)"
    },
    {
      "tag": "P",
      "text": "Visual learning paths from beginner introductions to advanced techniques",
